OL,3,CIslanders invited to express their
OL,4,Cviews on mental health services in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FResidents in Jersey are invited to
OL,8,Fexpress their views on adult mental
OL,9,Fhealth facilities on the island.
OL,11,FOn Thursday 12 November, an open
OL,12,Fmeeting will be held at St Helier Town
OL,13,FHall where islanders will hear what
OL,14,Fwork has been ongoing across Adult
OL,15,FMental Health Services for the last
OL,16,Ftwo years.
