OL,3,CIslanders invited to express their
OL,4,Cviews on mental health services in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FDirector of Mental Health, Social Care
OL,8,Fand Community Services Andy Weir says:
OL,9,F"We set out two and a half years ago
OL,10,Fon a programme of work to redesign,
OL,11,Fimprove and make changes across mental
OL,12,Fhealth services in Jersey.
OL,14,F"We had a public event where people
OL,15,Ftold us lots of things that they
OL,16,Fwanted us to do and we think it is now
OL,17,Ftime to come back and say what we have
OL,18,Fdone, what we are still working on and
OL,19,Fwhat islanders want next."
