OL,3,CIslanders invited to express their
OL,4,Cviews on mental health services in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FAndy Weir explains what residents
OL,8,Fwant, he says: "People want mental
OL,9,Fhealth services which are easily
OL,10,Faccessible, they want to be seen
OL,11,Fquickly when they need to be seen,
OL,12,Fthey want to receive a good quality of
OL,13,Fcare and I think they want to know
OL,14,Fwhat they can do to support people."
