OL,4,Cviews on mental health services in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FHe adds what he hopes islanders will
OL,8,Ftake to the meeting: "I want to hear
OL,9,Fhow people's experiences have been,
OL,10,FI'm hoping people can understand the
OL,11,Fwork that happens here, we hear a lot
OL,12,Fabout the stuff that is challenging
OL,13,Flike ADHD waiting lists, but we don't
OL,14,Fhear at all about the work the good
OL,15,Fwork that happens."
