OL,3,CIslanders invited to express their
OL,4,Cviews on mental health services in
OL,5,CJersey
OL,7,FHe also raises the common themes that
OL,8,Fhave been topical already, he
OL,9,Fexplains: "People want to be seen
OL,10,Fquickly, people want the consistency
OL,11,Fof care and one of the big issues is
OL,12,Faround dementia care and what the
OL,13,Ffuture of dementia care looks like."
OL,15,FAndy Weir adds he has been taking
OL,16,Finspiration from modules used
OL,17,Felsewhere, he says: "Over the last
OL,18,Fcouple of years we have been reshaping
OL,19,Four modules, but what is important is
OL,20,Fthat we do the right thing for Jersey
OL,21,Fand we meet the needs of people here.
